\id 2TH - Siroi NT with OT portions [ssd] -Papua New Guinea 1999 (web version -2013 bd) 
\h 2 TESALONIKA 
\toc1 Tesalonika mbal tuku waŋe Paulusŋge arnu kuyarna 
\toc2 2 Tesalonika 
\toc3 2Tes 
\mt1 2 TESALONIKA  
\mt2 Tesalonika mbal tuku waŋe Paulusŋge arnu kuyarna  
\ip Paulus nu Korinŋge minmba Tesalonika mbal tuku waŋe amboŋga kuyarna le yar ndui ta mbolŋge ndo nu maŋ lato waŋe arnu te kuyarmba pilna le nane tugum kina. Waŋe te tugunu ta teŋenmba.  
\ip Tesalonika mbal nane Paulus tuku waŋe amboŋga kuyarna ta burkinaig sulumba katese maye ndanaig. Nane Yesus luka prowam tuku pasa Paulusŋge kuyarna ta burkumba tugunu katese ndamba nu buk luka prona ŋga idusnaig. Ta tuku Paulus nu nane tuku wamdus purfeu serniŋgam tuku waŋe arnu te kuyarna.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Tane Mam Kuate le Suŋgo Yesus Kristus nale tuku mbal Tesalonikaŋge minig tane ŋakmba kaiye. Ye Paulus Silvanus le Timoteus sine tane ndoŋ pasa-pasakam proweg.  
\v 2 Mam Kuate le Suŋgo Yesus Kristus nale tane ake sinaŋ make patika ŋgamuŋgal wamdus bul sertiŋguwaik. Son.   
\s1 Wam kame Yesus tuku ait mbolŋge prowamŋgaig  
\p
\v 3 O tira kame, sine mara mara tane idustiŋmba Kuate gare pasa tuweg. Taŋgine ŋgamuŋgal son suŋgo ŋayote le tane taŋgine taŋgine lato lato muŋgu kume purkade tukunu sine Kuate gare pasa tuweg ta maŋau kumumbi keg.  
\v 4 Sine Kuate tuku kuasmbi ŋakmba ŋgamukŋge tane tuku suŋgomba saka payamkeg. Nane afu tane pitimbi tidoŋgade le rar kamusmba taŋgine ŋgamuŋgal son bike ndaka saŋgri tiŋgade wam ta tuku sine tane tuku payamka nane saniŋgeg.   
\p
\v 5 Kuate nu kumumbi tane piletiŋgit. Tane Kuate kulatkate ma mbol kambim tuku minig sulumba piti ta kaŋgerde. Nu piti tambi tane saŋgri piletiŋguwa le minap ma ma nu kulatkate ma mbol kaŋgaig.  
\v 6-7 Suŋgo Yesus nu nuŋe eŋel kame saŋgri ŋak nane ndoŋ samba mbolŋge pa mane suŋgo taŋaŋ mayok kuwaig le nane afu tane piti tiŋgig ta Kuate nu kumumba pa niŋgamŋgat.  
\v 8 Nu promba nane afu Kuate idus ndade mbal siŋgine Suŋgo Yesus tuku pasa mayenu pitaide mbal nane ŋakmba pa suŋgo niŋgamŋgat.  
\v 9 Nu nane pa niŋguwa le nane Suŋgo tuku tumail nuŋe kilŋa maŋ kaŋger ndamba mine ŋayonu mbolŋge minmba minamŋgaig.  
\v 10 Nu prowa le sine nuŋe mbal nu kaŋgermba mbariŋ-mbariŋmba nu tuku nyu suŋgo ta te-duŋgamŋgig. Sine tane ŋgamukŋge pasa kukligeŋ le tane son ŋginaig ta tane mata nu mbariŋamŋgaig.   
\p
\v 11 Sine wam ta idusmba mara mara tane tuku ŋga Kuate yabaŋeg. Nu tane nuŋe mbal mayok kambim tuku wikina ta tane nu am mbolŋge taŋamba mayok kape ŋga nu yabaŋeg. Tane buk taŋgine ŋgamuŋgal sonmbi wam magenu ŋakmba kam idusde tukunu Kuateŋge nu nuŋe saŋgri tiŋguwa le wam kame taŋamba mayok kuwaig ŋga iduseg.  
\v 12 Mayok kuwaig le Suŋgo Yesus Kristus tuku nyu tane ŋgamukŋge suŋgokuwa le tane nu mbolŋge mata nyu tamŋgaig. Siŋgine Kuate Suŋgo Yesus Kristus nale tane ake sinaŋ make patikade. Son.   
\c 2  
\s1 Une tuku tugu taŋgo  
\p
\v 1 O tira kame, Suŋgo Yesus Kristus prowa le sine ŋakmba nu tugumŋge maŋgurkamŋgig. Sine wam ta tuku pasa afu satiŋgamŋgig.  
\v 2 Ande nuŋe kiŋambi Yesus nu buk luka prona ŋga sakuwa ko Paulus nane taŋamba sakinaig ko kuyarnaig ŋga satiŋguwaig ndeta tane pasa ta ismba piriri ŋayomba ŋgamuŋgal piti ndatiŋguwa.  
\v 3 Tane riroŋkap. Nane afu tane yabritiŋbekaig. Yesus prowam tuku ait ta pro ndawa le amboŋga taŋgo pino ŋakmba wamdus ulendimba Kuate pitaiwaig le une tuku tugu taŋgo mayok kaŋgat. Taŋgo ta nu ŋgisikam tuku taŋgo.  
\v 4 Nu mayok ka taŋgo nu ndo mbariŋwaig ŋga idusmba taŋgo tuku mbara yimyam naŋgine mbariŋniŋgam tuku agaŋ kame ta ŋakmba ndoŋ ŋgueu minmba tidoŋ pankamŋgat. Nu Kuate tuku wande suŋgo sinamŋge minyok minmba ye ndo Kuate ŋga sakamŋgat.   
\p
\v 5 Ye tane ndoŋ minen sulumba wam ta tuku satiŋgen ta tane idus ndade?  
\v 6 Une tuku tugu taŋgo ta nuŋe ait kumuŋguwa le nu mayok kaŋgat. Saŋgri andeŋge nu mayok kambim tuku peute. Saŋgri ta tane kila.  
\v 7 Kile une tuku tugu taŋgo nu kuirkuirka piroka minit. Taŋamba minwa le ma ma saŋgri nu peumba minit ta nu kusrewamŋgat.  
\v 8 Kusrewa le une tuku tugu taŋgo nu mayok kaŋgat.  
\v 9 Mayok kuwa le Satan nu saŋgri yimyam tuwa le nu yabri wam kitek saŋgri ŋayo gudommba kile-mayokkamŋgat.  
\v 10 Taŋamba nu nane ŋgisikam tuku mbal tugumŋge maŋau ŋaigonu ke lika saŋgri tambi yabriniŋgamŋgat. Nane muskil kile-tidiŋge niŋgam tuku pasa tugusek ismba mbulmba pitaide tukunu nane ŋgisikam tuku minig.  
\v 11 Ta tuku Kuate nu nane tuku wamdus ŋginŋgan serniŋguwa le nane yabri maŋau ta kaŋgerka son ŋgamŋgaig.  
\v 12 Nane Kuate tuku pasa tugusek pitaide sulumba une maŋau kam tuku ŋgamuŋgal kunde-kundeniŋgig mbal Kuate nu nane pa ŋayonu niŋgamŋgat.   
\s1 Kuate nu Tesalonika mbal madiniŋgina  
\p
\v 13 O tira kame, sine tane idustiŋmba Kuate gare pasa tuweg. Nu tane tuku kume purte. Nu abo abo tane Tukul Guwa mbolŋge Kuate tuku mbal mayok ka pasa tugusek ismba son ŋgap le tane tuku muskil kile-tidiŋge tiŋgam tuku tane maditiŋgina.  
\v 14 Tane siŋgine Suŋgo Yesus Kristus tuku kilŋa saŋgri suŋgo tap ŋga sine tane ŋgamukŋge pasa mayenu kukligeŋ le Kuate nu tane wikina.   
\p
\v 15 O tira kame, tane wam ta idusmba bike ndaka saŋgri tiŋga siŋgine miŋgembi ko waŋembi Kuate tuku pasa satiŋgigeŋ ta dubi mageka bige dedeŋgap.   
\p
\v 16 Siŋgine Mam Kuate nu sine tuku suŋgomba kume purmba ake sinaŋ sine make patikate le sine wam mayenu tairŋga minmba ŋgamuŋgal mukuk ŋak mineg.  
\v 17 Siŋgine Suŋgo Yesus Kristus Mam Kuate nale tane wamdus saŋgri piletiŋguwaik le tane wam ke likade ko pasa sakade ta magenu kile-mayokkap ŋga Kuate yabaŋet. Son.   
\c 3  
\s1 Yabaŋam tuku pasa  
\p
\v 1 O tira kame, ye pasa te ndo satiŋgamŋgit. Suŋgo tuku pasa tane ŋgamukŋge suŋgokina taŋamba afu ŋgamukŋge suŋgokuwa ŋga tane sine tuku ŋga Kuate yabaŋap.  
\v 2 Kuate tuku pasa isig mbal afu son nda ŋgade. Ta tuku taŋgo ŋaigonu nane sine ŋaigo siglikubekaig ŋga Kuateŋge sine tursiŋgam tuku ŋga yabaŋap.   
\p
\v 3 Suŋgo nuŋge tane tuku ŋgamuŋgal saŋgri piletiŋgamŋgat. Nu tane kulatkuwa le Satan nu tane ŋaigo siglike nda.  
\v 4 Suŋgo nu wamdus siŋgina le sine tane tuku wamdus ar ar ndaweg. Sine wam pagu pasa buk satiŋgigeŋ ta tane taŋamba ndo ke lika minmba minamŋgaig ta sine kila.  
\v 5 Kuateŋge tane wamdus purfeu sertiŋguwa le nu tane tuku suŋgomba kume purte wam Yesus nu saŋgri tiŋga bike ndakina maŋau ta lato lato kila patika wamdus saŋgri tiŋgap ŋga ye tane tuku ŋga Kuate yabaŋet.   
\s1 Pirokam tuku pasa  
\p
\v 6 Tira kame, sine siŋgine Suŋgo Yesus Kristus tuku nyu mbolŋge wam pagu pasa te satiŋgamŋgig. Tira ande nu sine tane wam pagu tiŋgigeŋ pasa ta pitaimba piro ndaka ake kaloimba minwa kande tane nu ndoŋ ulendi ndakap.  
\v 7 Sine tane ŋgamukŋge mingeŋ ta ake kaloimba mine ndakigeŋ.  
\v 8 Sine afu tugumŋge nyamagaŋ ake yai ndakigeŋ. Sine ŋakmba piyamba kilgeŋ. Sine tane piti tiŋbekig ŋga ki furir mindek siŋgine waimbi piroka matuk kageŋ.   
\p
\v 9 Sine Kristus tuku piro mbal tukunu sine tane tuku agaŋ ndende ake kilam kumuŋ ta tane sine tuku maŋau ta kubemba taŋamba pirokap ŋga sine piroka tane tuku agaŋ ndende kile ndakigeŋ.  
\v 10 Sine tane ŋgamukŋge mingeŋ sulumba teŋenmba wam pagutiŋgigeŋ. Taŋgo ima nu piro ndaka ake minwa kande nu nyamagaŋ nye ndakuwa ŋgigeŋ.   
\p
\v 11 Tane tuku afu kanyummba ake kaloimba minig sulumba afu tuku wam kugerkade ta afuŋge kubede le sine iseg.  
\v 12 Sine Suŋgo Yesus Kristus tuku nyu mbolŋge mbal taŋaŋ wam pagu pasa tembi sarsarniŋgamŋgig. Nane wamdus bafukmbi piroka piro tuku piya tambi naŋgine nyamagaŋ piyawaig.   
\p
\v 13 Tira kame, tane wam magenu kam tuku kanyum ndawap.  
\v 14 Sine waŋe te pilbe le tane tugum prowa le ande nu sine tuku pasa te pitaiwa kande tane nu kaŋgermba kiko tuwa ŋga nu ndoŋ ulendi ndakap.  
\v 15 Nu tane tuku tira ta nu ŋgueu taŋgo taŋaŋ kaŋger ndamba nu riroŋ pasa tape.   
\s1 Kaiye pasa  
\p
\v 16 Ŋgamuŋgal mukuk wamdus bulok maŋau Suŋgo nu tugu. Nuŋge mara mara taŋgine mine ŋakmba tuku ŋgamuŋgal mukuk wam bul sertiŋguwa. Nu tane ŋakmba ndoŋ minwa. Son.   
\p
\v 17 Ye Paulus ye kile yiŋe waimbi kaiye pasa te kuyaramŋgit. Tane ŋakmba kaiye. Waŋe te ye tuku ŋga tane katesewam tuku ye yiŋe wai kuyar tuku maŋau pilet. Yiŋe waŋe ŋakmba mbolŋge ye taŋawet.   
\p
\v 18 Siŋgine Suŋgo Yesus Kristus nu tane ŋakmba ake sinaŋ make patikuwa.  
\p Son.   